snippet.title: 11-11: Memories Retold -  PS4 / X1 / PC - Harry and Kurt Trailer
snippet.description:
"It's either him or me."

Join us on November 9th, 2018, for a story of war that crosses the barriers between loyalties, languages, and nations.  Starring Elijah Wood and Sebastian Koch.
